name: Shri Lakshmi Labelss
overview: Shri Lakshmi Labelss is a partnership firm, started its business in 2010 as a manufacturer, exporter and supplier of a broad range of Labels, Hang Tags and Stickers. Our products encompass Barcode Stickers, Prismatic Stickers, Woven Garment Labels, Heat Transfer Labels, Fabric Woven Labels, Heat Transfer Labels, Die Cut Hang Tags, Bamboo Hang Tags and many others. By following the guidelines of total quality management system, our company has been able to maintain steadiness and constant flow of quality approved range in the market. Our products can also be customized according to the specified demands of clients. Reckoned for their exceptional features like durability, weatherproof, attractiveness, Eco-friendliness and others, our range has found its large application all across the globe. We are getting repeated orders from our clients, which show our capability of delivering quality approved and desired product range in the market.
